parameters:
Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'Welcome, warriors of the Empire! To
defeat our warriors, you must be quite skilled!'

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Hahaha, I'll show respect as a fellow
warrior.

Clea: I have a favor to ask today. I would like to use the
Bulk Gang's territory as a transportation route.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Hmm, that matter was previously
discussed and ended in failure.
Clea: Could you please tell me the reason?

Goat of the Bulk Gang: For us, the forest is a place where
the souls of our predecessors rest. Only the warriors
recognized by the Bulk Gang are allowed to pass through
there.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: If it's for transportation purposes,
even merchants should be allowed to pass through. But we
cannot permit that.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: What's wrong, we're in the middle of
a conversation?

Goat of the Bulk Gang: ...I apologize, warriors, but we're
running out of time.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: I apologize, but I cannot accept this
request as a warrior of the Bulk Gang.

Clea (The negotiation has failed, so let's go meet with
someone named Ruid next.)

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Valt Region / Mansion of the
Profligate Nobles\c[0]
Warriors, welcome to the Bulk Gang's hideout!

Cleric Sophia: The question we have... Can you answer it
today?

Mage Relm: That's right! I can't believe an ogre can become
human!

Bulk Gang's Goat: Mage... it's the opposite... It's not that
the ogre became human, it's that the human becomes an ogre.

Bulk Gang's Goat: That ogre was a warrior of the Bulk Gang
and my best friend who grew up together in this place.
Clea: ...I'm sorry for what I've done.

Bulk Gang's Goat: No, it doesn't matter. It would be my wish
to be defeated by exceptional warriors like you.
Bulk Gang's Goat: Did he leave any last words?
Clea: Thank you... He said that with a satisfied voice.

Bulk Gang's Goat: I see... He was able to pass away
satisfied.

Bulk Gang's Goat: Do you have any wishes that this goat, who
owes you a great debt, can fulfill?
Clea: Do you have any wishes...?

Thief Nora: How about the right to accept requests in the
Valt region?

Thief Nora: Ah, I'm sorry! It's nothing, never mind. I
apologize!

Bulk Gang's Goat: Hahaha, I don't have any desires! If
that's okay with you, feel free to accept requests.

Bulk Gang's Goat: I may not be able to fully repay this debt
with just this, but if you ever have any troubles, feel free
to come here anytime!
実績 深林の冒険者

Goat from the Bulk Gang: 'If you ever have any problems,
feel free to come here anytime!'
Bulk Gang's Goat: Ughhh... calm down... ughhhh!

Bulk Gang's Goat: Huff... huff... damn it... Goddess
Actina... why do you subject us to such trials...

Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'If you ever have any problems, feel
free to come here anytime!'

Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'Oh, warriors! What brings you here
today?'
Clea: Actually, we came here with a consultation.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Tell me! I'll do anything I can to
help!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Not just ogres, but dragons too!?
You're not teasing me, are you... I apologize.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: If you look into your eyes, you'll
understand that dragons exist and are in the Monimos
Mountains.

Clea: Please lend us your strength. We need people who will
join forces with us to reach the dragons.
Thief Nora: Please count me in too!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: As a proud warrior who took care of
my dear friend, Valto, I will cooperate with you.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: The place where the Bulk Gang resides
is a battlefield. If it becomes the largest battlefield in
the empire, we must go!
Thief Nora: We did it! Thank you very much!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Hahaha, let's meet on the
battlefield!

events.name: EV013イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼1-6

parameters:
Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'It is a very important matter for us
to apologize for the rudeness.'

Priestess Sophia: We have come as messengers of the
priestess of Imiserinos.
Goat of the Bulk Gang: ...What did you just say?

Priestess Sophia: We are messengers of the priestess of
Imiserinos--
Goat of the Bulk Gang: You're not the priestess of Actina!?

Goat of the Bulk Gang: So you're not the priestess of
Actina... Are you really here as messengers of the priestess
of Imiserinos?

Priestess Sophia: Yes, we are messengers of the priestess of
Imiserinos.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: I see, so the goddess Actina has
abandoned me.

Priestess Sophia: I felt that there was something
intentionally hidden in the story of my best friend
transforming into an ogre.

Priestess Sophia: If you could tell us the story, there
might be something we can help with.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Let me tell you everything... about
the curse that has long plagued the Bulk Gang.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: In the Bulk Gang, occasionally there
are individuals who transform into ogres. Each time, it
falls upon close associates to subdue them.
Clea: The ones we defeated as well...

Goat of the Bulk Gang: He is also a victim of the curse, and
I myself have also begun to be consumed by the curse.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: There are priests and mages who want
to break the curse that plagues the Bulk Gang. They want to
request assistance to find a solution.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: It's impossible for me to solve this
on my own...!

Priestess Sophia: Of course, it is also a request from the
priestess of Imiserinos.

Mage Relm: The Bulk Gang should have little to do with
magic... There must be something special influencing them...

Goat of the Bulk Gang: If it becomes impossible to resolve
the situation with warriors and thieves, I want you to
subdue the [monsters].

Goat of the Bulk Gang: It's not that I don't trust my
comrades, but I can trust you since you defeated the dragon.

Clea: I will definitely find a way to prevent that from
happening.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: There isn't much time left. The curse
is definitely reaching my soul.
